-\eta\partial_{x}^{2}-\mu & V_{\text{Z}}+\alpha_{\text{R}}\partial_{x}\\
V_{\text{Z}}-\alpha_{\text{R}}\partial_{x} & -\eta\partial_{x}^{2}-\mu
\end{array}\right)\label{eq:h_true}\\
\boldsymbol{\Delta}\equiv & \left(\Delta_{0}\Theta(x-L)+\Theta(-x-L)e^{\textcolor{red}{\pm}i\varphi}\right)\mathds{1}\label{eq:d_true}
