\begin_inset Formula $x\lessgtr0$
\end_inset

 to be normalized whilst forcing the boundary conditions 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\Psi}(0^{-})=\bar{\Psi}(0^{+})$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{x}\bar{\Psi}(0^{+})=\partial_{x}\bar{\Psi}(0^{+})$
\end_inset

